                    "prompt": "Bob would like to encrypt a message for Alice using secret key (or symmetric) encryption, and then securely share the secret key with Alice using public key (or asymmetric) encryption. Select the correct order in which the following steps must occur:<br><br>A. Bob sends the encrypted key and message to Alice.<br>B. Bob encrypts the symmetric key with Alice's public key.<br>C. Alice uses the symmetric key to decrypt the message.<br>D. Bob encrypts the message with the symmetric key.<br>E. Alice uses her private key to decrypt the symmetric key.",
                    "ignored": false,
                    "mode": "radio",
                    "choices": [
                        {
                            "id": "choice1",
                            "text": "A, C, D, E, B"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "choice2",
                            "text": "B, E, D, C, A"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "choice3",
                            "text": "D, B, A, E, C"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "choice4",
